cc;\"\n| style=\"background:#98fb98;\"|Win || 1956 || Australian Championships || Grass || {{flagicon|AUS}} Thelma Coyne Long || {{flagicon|AUS}} [[Mary Carter Reitano]] <br> {{flagicon|AUS}} Beryl Penrose || 6\u20132, 5\u20137, 9\u20137\n|- style=\"background:#ffffcc;\"\n| style=\"background:#ffa07a;\"|Loss || 1957 || Australian Championships || Grass || {{flagicon|AUS}} [[Fay Muller]] || {{flagicon|USA}} [[Shirley Fry]] <br> {{flagicon|USA}} [[Althea Gibson]] || 2\u20136, 1\u20136\n|- style=\"background:#cfc;\"\n| style=\"background:#ffa07a;\"|Loss || 1957 || Wimbledon || Grass || {{flagicon|AUS}} [[Thelma Coyne Long]] || {{flagicon|USA}} Althea Gibson <br> {{flagicon|USA}} [[Darlene Hard]] ||  1\u20136, 2\u20136\n|- style=\"background:#ffffcc;\"\n| style=\"background:#98fb98;\"|Win || 1958 || Australian Championships || Grass || {{flagicon|AUS}} Thelma Coyne Long || {{flagicon|AUS}} [[Lorraine Coghlan]] <br> {{flagicon|GBR}} [[Angela Mortimer]] || 7\u20135, 6\u20138, 6\u20132\n|- style=\"background:#ebc2af;\"\n|style=\"background:#ffa07a;\"|Loss || 1958 || French Championships || Clay ||{{flagicon|AUS}} Thelma Coyne Long || {{flagicon|MEX}} [[Yola Ram\u00edrez]] <br> {{flagicon|MEX}} [[Rosie Reyes]] || 4\u20136, 5\u20137\n|- style=\"background:#ffffcc;\"\n| style=\"background:#ffa07a;\"|Loss || 1961 || Australian Championships || Grass || {{flagicon|AUS}} [[Jan Lehane]] || {{flagicon|AUS}} Mary Carter Reitano <br> {{flagicon|AUS}} [[Margaret Smith Court|Margaret Smith]] || 4\u20136, 6\u20133, 5\u20137\n|}\n\n===Mixed doubles: 2 (1\u20131)===\n{|class=\"sortable wikitable\" \n!style=\"width:40px\"|Result\n!style=\"width:30px\"|Year\n!style=\"width:165px\"|Championship\n!style=\"width:50px\"|Surface\n!style=\"width:190px\"|Partner\n!style=\"width:190px\"|Opponents\n!style=\"width:140px\" class=\"unsortable\"|Score\n|-style=\"background:#ffffcc;\"\n| style=\"background:#ffa07a;\"|Loss || 1956 || Australian Championships || Grass || {{flagicon|AUS}} [[Roy Emerson]] |